      "bullets": [
        "GameLift Streams now supports IAM roles via the RoleArn parameter, replacing insecure, long-lived embedded access keys for stream sessions.",
        "Uses the container credential provider mechanism—similar to ECS task roles and EKS Pod Identity—to automatically refresh short-lived AWS tokens.",
        "Role misconfigurations are validated instantly at session startup, preventing runtime errors and streamlining AWS service access (e.g., S3, DynamoDB)."
